Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:42.56,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! We need more over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:43.36,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:44.43,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Where's that bonbori?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:45.63,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.63,0:01:46.98,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.66,0:01:53.79,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana, are you done over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.79,0:01:55.26,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Um... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.15,0:02:01.27,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's such a shame when you're getting so many reservations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.27,0:02:02.28,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.67,0:02:05.22,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! What are you going to write on your wishing plaque?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:08.86,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't really thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:11.39,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,What? You should get on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.39,0:02:12.90,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it really works.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:14.82,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Makes dreams and ambitions come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:16.51,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.51,0:02:17.65,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.02,0:02:20.41,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,I want to study abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:23.92,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,I want to learn about the hotel situation overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:25.03,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:32.18,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A goddess takes everyone's wishes to the sky{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:36.58,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}as thanks for lighting her up with bonbori...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:42.59,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I came to Yunosagi, I felt like I wanted to shine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:51.60,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then the days flew by, and I came to like my work and Kissuiso.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:54.07,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But what's my dream...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:55.86,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:57.47,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.47,0:02:58.91,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Almost forgot, Ohana!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:01.46,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:09.85,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,With this many people, we have a lot to prepare for dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:13.34,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,so we don't want to overwork ourselves serving breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.34,0:03:14.17,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:18.81,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,With that in mind, we'll have to make the breakfast a buffet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:19.70,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:20.55,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.73,0:03:24.49,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Well... We have people saying
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they like how they can take their time in their own—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:28.47,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Just live with it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:30.24,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have enough staff in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:30.98,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Minko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:34.89,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning after the guests check out will also be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.89,0:03:36.82,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,The girls also have school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.39,0:03:40.26,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stop assigning rooms, and I'll also help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:42.24,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,You took more reservations?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:44.20,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:46.66,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:49.53,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the other inns are doing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fine and they have more guests than we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:54.48,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can run an inn if you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all overwork yourselves together?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:04:00.46,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying we'll lower the quality of our service!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.96,0:04:03.23,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,We're just finding new ways to make ends meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:06.28,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Food is still food in a buffet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:08.90,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,We'll still cook the way we used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:10.55,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,The service won't go down either!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.55,0:04:13.44,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,With no one in charge of one room, I'll oversee everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.87,0:04:21.32,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:22.28,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:23.45,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will do as we've always done for the Bonbori Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:34.08,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,We're not backing down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:35.35,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The Kissuiso I Love
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.46,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:49.18,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I brought some wishing plaques.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:57.13,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Here. You... write your wish and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:53.41,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:54.20,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:58.46,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:04:59.88,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Ohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:01.83,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,We're too busy for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:05.24,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Nako!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:15.17,Default,Mameji,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, I'll have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:19.21,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like it's not quite right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:24.22,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I want the Kissuiso to stay open as much as everyone else does.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.65,0:05:28.79,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Minchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:30.32,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:34.35,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Stop siding with the Madam Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:36.24,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm on her side!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:37.27,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:39.72,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,You have a place to go back to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:41.77,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,A place to go back to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:44.91,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:45.90,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,This is my home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:48.36,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about the Bonbori Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:52.62,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,This is where my dream is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:54.43,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:59.71,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,You made me happy when I thought you felt the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:02.46,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Minchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.58,0:06:06.77,Default,Mameji,0000,0000,0000,,You're all good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:11.41,Default,Mameji,0000,0000,0000,,All of you here are good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:33.95,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Nakochi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:35.46,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:38.39,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd also sleep here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:39.85,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:43.53,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I don't mind, but are you sure you're okay on the floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:45.81,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get here in the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and everyone's working hard, so I also...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:52.14,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Working hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.88,0:06:55.06,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, maybe, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:57.79,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,They're not festing it up... I don't think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:58.68,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:01.11,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:04.43,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you're going to sleep there, sleep in my—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:06.66,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Nako, get to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:08.03,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Minichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:08.03,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Work starts at 4 tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.03,0:07:09.63,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,4?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.63,0:07:11.95,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,It's already past midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.04,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:26.96,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nakochi's sleeping over, but we can't even talk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.89,0:07:31.72,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything feels too tight...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:35.24,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I... don't really like it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.26,0:07:47.86,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:53.74,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have time to be taking a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:07:55.51,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,You're helping too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:59.29,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give everyone a word in about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:02.20,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,You'll just feel left out siding with the Madam Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:06.84,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not that I'm siding with anyone. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:09.88,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to restore the Kissuiso?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:11.55,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Just listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:14.23,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:19.77,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,You usually butt in on everyone's business
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and make the whole place fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:23.86,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:25.12,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:30.73,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Kissuiso didn't change. You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.82,0:08:43.80,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,First, bring the guests to the main hall and identify their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:46.55,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to call, too. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:47.26,Default,Two,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:48.24,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:50.48,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,That's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:52.41,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Take this please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.41,0:08:54.84,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:08:59.67,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Nako. More rice porridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:00.60,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:04.29,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this dish is top notch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:07.90,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,You don't usually get this kind of food in a buffet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.40,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:13.72,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The food's top notch and made with seasonal ingredients,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:17.54,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,and people still love the food, but...{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:20.28,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:23.96,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Say, is breakfast only served as buffet now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:26.55,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:32.47,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I liked how we could relax at this inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:34.67,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is fun too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:38.75,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, can you leave some room in-between?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:40.24,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:42.51,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a little more to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:44.06,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:48.77,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm making an art gallery of some local artists.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:51.44,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,This will get us guests and profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:53.24,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Just you watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:55.18,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Kissuiso is going to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:58.07,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana, you also- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:02.24,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kissuiso is going to change...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:06.40,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I wanted to show Ko{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Bonbori Festival and the Kissuiso I love...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.79,0:10:16.84,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,I see... a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:18.93,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:21.34,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,We can't take any more reservations, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.84,0:10:23.50,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,If this room will suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.09,0:10:26.23,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,This room?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.53,0:10:28.45,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,You want to show him the Kissuiso, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.76,0:10:32.30,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Then he can stay here as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:35.89,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:38.92,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Is your health okay? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.92,0:10:39.66,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:43.74,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I've never seen you so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.78,0:10:49.05,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,He's an important friend, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:51.42,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:53.58,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.94,0:10:56.34,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Tsurugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:11:00.21,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Minko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:02.82,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Tohru—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:05.89,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,I got a glimpse of the princess sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:07.83,Default,Boy2,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Tohru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:16.15,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:17.78,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Minchi—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:17.78,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:21.82,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,You know what that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:23.82,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,She's sulking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:27.83,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're siding with the Madam Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.47,0:11:31.54,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Tsurugi likes you, Ohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:38.05,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,That's hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:40.30,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,How's the soup stock?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:41.75,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Checking right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:43.25,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Minko, wash the vegetables!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:44.05,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:47.82,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,When you're done with that, get the duck ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:48.75,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:53.88,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can still be a cook whereever I go. Tohru's right about that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:57.27,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... I want to stay here{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}because Tohru's here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:01.61,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Ren's here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.23,0:12:04.99,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone's... here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:07.32,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Balut!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.32,0:12:09.50,Default,Two,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we're serving something that eerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:10.81,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:11.76,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mr. Ren!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.76,0:12:12.33,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:13.57,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,You tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:16.86,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,The bowls aren't out, and the guests are complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:22.40,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm having an easy time having to change the soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:24.38,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying it's my fault?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:23.88,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Mr. Ren...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:27.10,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! What's going on with you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:25.65,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you waitresses get the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,bowls out or something before you make excuses?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:29.93,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to be arguing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:29.07,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Say that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:31.39,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,This is the kitchen's problem! Not blame us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.39,0:12:32.64,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Your heart's like tofu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:34.44,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just sensitive! Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:35.11,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,With that face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:36.44,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a pure, innocent, sensitive...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.11,0:12:36.44,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:39.53,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to protect the inn?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:43.49,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a crucial time for us right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:45.90,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't fight here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.21,0:12:48.37,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:57.18,Default,Two,0000,0000,0000,,Have a great trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:58.13,Default,Two2,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:12:59.38,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Dear, say bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:01.16,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:05.35,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Something doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.11,0:13:09.93,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I like the Kissuiso.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:13.10,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me happy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.53,0:13:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when everyone's doing their best to make the guests happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:22.04,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,But... it's not the same anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.04,0:13:24.97,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's too focused on the Madam Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:30.81,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana, you know her real intentions, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.14,0:13:34.40,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:35.94,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:41.17,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,She's the very person who founded the Kissuiso I love!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:43.15,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Nakochi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:49.64,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Stuck with her dream, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:50.63,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.61,0:13:54.14,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,She just doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:13:56.86,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Because she's a runner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:14:00.06,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Some people can't have their own dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:05.53,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,but they can follow someone else's dream
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and make it their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yunosagi Springs
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:26.09,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:27.52,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.52,0:14:29.43,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Did you already come up with a wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.73,0:14:30.94,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.94,0:14:34.60,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,And what happened to the Kissuiso's wishing plaques?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:36.23,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,I gave them to you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:38.73,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Well... they seem to be busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:40.24,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:42.94,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana, they're taking advantage of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.21,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:45.44,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.74,0:14:48.26,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,I will go get them for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:50.52,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait up, Yuina!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.78,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,I will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.17,0:14:54.64,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:53.87,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuina!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:14:59.85,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Tomoe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:09.22,Default,Taxi,0000,0000,0000,,During the festivals, we get people from all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.72,Default,Taxi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you from Tokyo, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:13.89,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:17.39,Default,Taxi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you have that city grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:19.08,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Do I really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:20.98,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:23.33,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Beanman! That really hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.33,0:15:24.22,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:25.73,Default,Mameji,0000,0000,0000,,It's sprained.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:28.51,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,How will we get by like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.51,0:15:30.66,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,We'll ask the union for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.66,0:15:32.11,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.52,0:15:34.29,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,We also asked for help,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but no one can help since it's before the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:38.21,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:39.95,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,The Madam Manager said that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have to do everything the way we used to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the Bonbori Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.95,0:15:45.63,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,That was part of the promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:47.28,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,That's just impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:49.38,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to beg her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:52.10,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,We can get by if we use the new way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:53.64,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:55.58,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,No! You need to stay put!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:57.53,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stay put!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:16:01.01,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to lose to the Madam Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:03.98,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to lose... to the Madam Manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:07.69,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Was work a battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:08.69,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:10.35,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,It's just wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:12.36,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Is it more important to win than
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,make the guests feel comfortable?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:17.22,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,If we lose, the Kissuiso will close!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:17.86,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:18.79,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really understand that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:19.95,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Please just stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:22.68,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Nako...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:26.29,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I love the Kissuiso.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:27.38,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I really do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:30.38,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,But this isn't the Kissuiso.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:33.93,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Please bring back the Kissuiso I love!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:35.50,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.50,0:16:40.10,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I... finally found a place I could be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:46.31,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,"I love the Kissuiso."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.68,0:16:50.07,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone there felt the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:53.75,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yet somehow, their feelings slipped past each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:57.12,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kissuiso... 'Tis a castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:17:00.47,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,in a long lost dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:04.37,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:07.33,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I was just speaking your thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.45,0:17:10.41,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it in your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:12.97,Default,Everyone,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:15.59,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work as a waitress.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:18.55,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,I should be able to fill in for Tomoe to an extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.96,0:17:20.78,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:24.39,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:25.64,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:28.36,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I came again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:29.65,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:31.04,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I needed a change of scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:32.86,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Staying for 2 nights. One adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:36.80,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, we're full right now, and we don't have time for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:39.62,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! I'll sleep in Ohana's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:42.31,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,If you let me stay, I'll help out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:46.54,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,You were yelling in that argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:50.05,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,And why is no one at the front desk when you should be busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:51.66,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, are you really going to help out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.66,0:17:52.80,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,No, you aren't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:55.38,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Enishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:58.48,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,This is our fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:18:02.56,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,If you or the Madam Manager help—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:06.28,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:08.31,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run on your emotions!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.66,0:18:11.13,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to save the Kissuiso?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.47,0:18:12.52,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Takky...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:17.03,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Enishing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:32.77,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,And... it's the day of the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:41.32,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, can I have that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:46.99,Default,Waitresses,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:56.48,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:18:59.77,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Takky, the Moon Room needs—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:01.45,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,You're busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.07,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Ask my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:04.33,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:07.20,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master, the Moon Room?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:07.83,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,What do they need?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.84,0:19:12.99,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,The yukata's too small. They want size L.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:14.21,Default,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:16.44,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:17.47,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:21.10,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a waitress today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:23.55,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,You need to give the orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:26.24,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:27.47,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,You have the wrong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:29.81,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the Madam Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:36.08,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm counting on you, Sui.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.61,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Minko, how's the vinegar dish?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:39.99,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Just needs the final toppings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:41.71,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Grill dish is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:42.70,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:45.03,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Can I get the Wave Room next?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.41,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.96,0:19:49.27,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Nako, I can take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:50.12,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:52.37,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,I can still clean with a sprained ankle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:53.93,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Can you take care of the banquet hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:55.59,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.29,0:20:01.63,Default,Two,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Good. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:03.47,Default,Two,0000,0000,0000,,And stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:05.68,Default,Two,0000,0000,0000,,You're all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:08.81,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I need to check the Crane Room next...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:12.02,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:13.31,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:15.66,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:17.51,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt a little dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.51,0:20:19.74,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you should rest a little—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:24.06,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,In an inn business, the guests come first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:26.37,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,We worry about ourselves last.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:31.88,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,But I enjoyed that kind of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:33.12,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:35.90,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go back to your own job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:38.56,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.36,0:20:45.47,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:47.46,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Can you get the stuffing in?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:48.33,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
